        \DB::table('posts')->delete();

        \DB::table('posts')->insert(array (
            0 =>
            array (
                'id' => 1,
                'title' => 'Meet the Xerocon Brisbane team',
            'content' => '{"time":1567333202387,"blocks":[{"type":"paragraph","data":{"text":"One of the best things about attending Xerocon is the chance to grow your network, put faces to names and build valuable relationships."}},{"type":"paragraph","data":{"text":"As a global cloud-based company, we also love the opportunity to spend some time \\u2018on the ground\\u2019 with our partners, getting to know you a little better, meeting new accountants and finding out more about your business."}},{"type":"paragraph","data":{"text":"If you\\u2019re heading along to Xerocon Brisbane, we\\u2019d love you to stop by the Figured stand to meet us! Here\\u2019s a quick introduction of who\\u2019s who in the zoo."}},{"type":"header","data":{"text":"Dave Dodds - CEO","level":5}},{"type":"paragraph","data":{"text":"Anyone in a room with Dave can\\u2019t help but get inspired by his energy - especially when it comes to spreading the word about Figured. He\\u2019s excited to be in town for Xerocon, seeing the impact that Xero and Figured is making on the agri-advisory scene. And we\\u2019re sure you\\u2019ll get a buzz from him too - once you\\u2019ve had a chance to chat to Dave you\\u2019ll see he\\u2019s always happy to share his energy, vision and drive for connecting farmers with their advisors to lift the financial performance of farmers around the globe."}},{"type":"header","data":{"text":"John Gibson - GM, NZ &amp; AU","level":5}},{"type":"paragraph","data":{"text":"Born and bred in Southland, John is a country boy from New Zealand\'s rural heartland, with a passion for technology\\u2019s ability to transform the industry. This, paired with a background in the agri sector working for one of New Zealand\\u2019s largest lamb and beef exporters, means John is inspired by the opportunities that Figured has to make farming rock. John is excited to see you all at Xerocon and make sure we\\u2019re giving you the best ag-tech experience you can get!&nbsp;"}},{"type":"header","data":{"text":"Jimmy Forward - Customer Success Lead, AU","level":5}},{"type":"paragraph","data":{"text":"Jimmy\'s role is to oversee the implementation of key projects and partnerships for Figured in Australia. He loves all things cloud, and solving real world problems with technology, so he\\u2019s our Figured product guru of the event. For anything product related or if you want a deep dive into Figured, be sure to keep an eye out for Jimmy - he\\u2019s got you covered."}},{"type":"header","data":{"text":"Dave McGregor - Business Development Manager, NZ","level":5}},{"type":"paragraph","data":{"text":"Dave is responsible for growing our relationships with our NZ partners and ensuring they have the right tools and tech they need to succeed. He\\u2019s hopping over the ditch to help make sure all our Kiwi partners feel at home amongst the Aussies - and of course to chat about how you can use the Figured product to step into the advisory opportunity."}},{"type":"header","data":{"text":"Chris Vanderkolk - Head of Marketing","level":5}},{"type":"paragraph","data":{"text":"Chris is passionate about New Zealand\\u2019s growing global presence on the tech scene, as well as the contribution our farmers have to feeding the world\'s population. As our Marketing expert, he can help you figure out how you can market Figured to new clients, and how you can grow your practise through marketing and comms activity - he\\u2019s also down for some good ol\\u2019 fashioned yarns."}},{"type":"header","data":{"text":"Dina Veljanovska - Marketing Communications Manager","level":5}},{"type":"paragraph","data":{"text":"Dina is responsible for our comms and running our marketing campaigns, and is very passionate about giving you the right tools and materials to explain the value of Figured to new clients. She\'ll be at Xerocon ready for a chat about how you\'re going with your journey to advisory, and how you\'re finding the Figured product. So if you\'re keen to feature on our social channels or website with any of your insights (or banter!) then keep an eye out for her.&nbsp;"}},{"type":"list","data":{"style":"unordered","items":["testing","testing","testing","testing"]}}],"version":"2.15.0"}',
                'created_at' => '2019-09-01 06:54:46',
                'updated_at' => '2019-09-01 10:20:02',
            ),
            1 =>
            array (
                'id' => 2,
                'title' => 'Exploring the advisory opportunity at Xerocon',
            'content' => '{"time":1567333838406,"blocks":[{"type":"paragraph","data":{"text":"As new technology streamlines compliance and automates manual accounting work, pressure amounts on accountants to figure out new ways to add value to their clients. With software like Xero and Figured, accountants have the perfect platform to start exploring the value of advisory services."}},{"type":"paragraph","data":{"text":"Xerocon is the perfect opportunity for you to engage with us, to find out how the Xero, Figured proposition can open the door to advisory services for your agri clients. You could take a bigger part in your client\\u2019s business."}},{"type":"paragraph","data":{"text":"How? Because our platform gives you back your valuable time. With data flowing between Xero and Figured, it streamlines your compliance work and tax planning, provides you with a single, ongoing financial plan to work with and draw reports from, and you can whip up a 5 year plan for your client\\u2019s business using our scenarios tool. We\\u2019re also releasing a new cropping experience where you have a new tracker and planning functionality for your arable clients."}},{"type":"paragraph","data":{"text":"Check out how our features can help you perform advisory services."}},{"type":"header","data":{"text":"Benchmarking &amp; Scenarios","level":2}},{"type":"paragraph","data":{"text":"Our benchmarking tool gives farmers and their advisors data that is refined beyond industry-wide benchmarks, so they can actually compare their performance against farms in their own area. It helps farming teams understand how their farm is performing in relation to those nearby, how well it\\u2019s being managed, and how sustainably it is run."}},{"type":"paragraph","data":{"text":"You can configure whatever metrics you\\u2019d like to compare, and decide whether it\\u2019s private for you or open to anyone at Figured to see. This gives you the ability to start conversations about how your client\\u2019s farm is performing and make decisions that\\u2019ll help them run a more profitable business."}},{"type":"paragraph","data":{"text":"Our scenarios planning tool allows you to plan a multi-year, 3-way view (P&amp;L, cashflow and balance sheet) of the farming operation. You can create \\u2018what if\\u2019 scenarios to assess different opportunities quickly and see how a farming business might look a few years ahead, based on a major financial proposition or variances in commodity prices, without having to complete a full cash flow budget. This gives you financial clarity around decision making, facilitating better conversations with clients."}},{"type":"header","data":{"text":"Cropping","level":2}},{"type":"paragraph","data":{"text":"This year at our stand, we\\u2019ll be showing you a brand new version of Figured\\u2019s cropping functionality."}},{"type":"paragraph","data":{"text":"Our new experience will enable your clients to easily plan and manage their crop season production and sales activities. This will be a whole new experience from an advisor perspective as you\\u2019ll understand their financial position more clearly"}},{"type":"paragraph","data":{"text":"We\\u2019re delighted to share this new experience with you, so we\\u2019d love to have you come by and check it out, and let us know what you think."}},{"type":"header","data":{"text":"Snapshots &amp; the Rolling Plan","level":2}},{"type":"paragraph","data":{"text":"This recently released feature allows you to build and maintain a single, ongoing financial plan, while keeping a record of all the changes you\\u2019ve made as you\\u2019ve moved through the year."}},{"type":"paragraph","data":{"text":"With the Rolling Plan functionality, you can get started on financial planning by adding to your existing plan, meaning you don\\u2019t need to spend your valuable time on building the initial budget or opening position. Instead of isolated budget years, you build on existing actuals from Xero, adding as much or as little detail as you like, and planning across any period of time. Once you\\u2019re happy with the plan you can take a Snapshot of your work to turn it into your Annual Plan."}},{"type":"paragraph","data":{"text":"You can also reforecast regularly and easily while keeping a record of changes to keep your team in the loop, as Snapshots provide a record of your financial plan at a point in time that can be used for comparative reporting. If conditions change throughout the year and you need to reforecast, simply rework the plan and save it as a new Snapshot."}},{"type":"paragraph","data":{"text":"You can also get more powerful reports out of Figured faster and simpler, allowing for comparative reporting and more valuable conversations between the entire farming team. We wanted to create a tool to facilitate these interactions so that the entire farming team can be involved in financial planning of the farm."}},{"type":"header","data":{"text":"Streamlined compliance","level":2}},{"type":"paragraph","data":{"text":"Move your practice beyond processing numbers at year-end and spend less time gathering information from your clients to complete compliance tasks. Figured provides a connected approach with your clients, and real-time reporting with high quality data flowing in from Xero and bank feeds, so that all your client\\u2019s information is in one place."}},{"type":"paragraph","data":{"text":"This ultimately improves efficiency and productivity, so that you can spend more time providing advisory services and developing stronger relationships with your clients."}},{"type":"paragraph","data":{"text":"We believe we have the best agri-advisory platform to help you play a bigger part in your clients business."}},{"type":"paragraph","data":{"text":"Come along to our stand at Xerocon to get a demo of these new features, a sneak preview at what\\u2019s to come, and a chance to give us feedback."}},{"type":"paragraph","data":{"text":"Check out what\\u2019s in store at&nbsp;<b>Xerocon<\\/b>&nbsp;this year."}}],"version":"2.15.0"}',
                'created_at' => '2019-09-01 10:30:38',
                'updated_at' => '2019-09-01 10:30:38',
            ),
        ));
    }
